Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:26.65,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,あのあのどんな色が　今ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.19,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑顔のホワイト　涙のブルー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.96,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,重ねてみたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:37.45,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,本日晴天なりっ　キャンパスに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.92,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,ミルクのアイス　ラムネごくん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.73,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,元気にカラートッピング
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.56,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,おーい！　ラブ描き·ぷりーす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:52.71,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなの似顔絵コンテスト
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:59.92,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,よーし！　後で「ぷんっ」怒らないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:05.05,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,スイッチ押されたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.17,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,わっはっは～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.49,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかいいキモチ　なればいいカンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.93,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,競争だ！　いち早くリンゴ食べよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:24.21,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,そうじゃないんだよ　躁でいいんだよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.88,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,果物はモデルさん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:36.94,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,さあデッサンしましょうか　宿題だよん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:26.65,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,请问请问　现在是什么颜色呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.19,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容的白色　泪水的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.96,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,将它们重叠在一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:37.45,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气晴朗　外出郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.92,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,进行冰牛奶弹珠汽水特训
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.73,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,代表精神的颜色正充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.56,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,喂－！　喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:52.71,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,请来进行大家的肖像画素描比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:59.92,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,好－吧！　之后可别「砰」的一下就生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:05.05,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,被人按下按钮时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.17,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.49,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得只要开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.93,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛吧　看谁苹果吃得快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:24.21,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样　急躁起来好吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.88,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,水果便是模特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:36.94,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,来　开始素描吧　这是作业哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:46.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天运势最佳的是水瓶座
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,日间的努力被认可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎能更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:53.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,双鱼座的环境有改善的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,向父母求助的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个节目好久没有看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待在家里的时候不会起这么早的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,白羊座  今天梦想似乎和你若即若离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:01.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要太过勉强为好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  作上学准备的时候总是错过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,金牛座  注意不要乱花钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的运势…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,巨蟹座似乎需要小心注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}今天的运势\N射手座\N很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,…反而接二连三地有事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:23.94,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,静下心来深呼吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家  今天也请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷吧  快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  天气预报说会下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会下雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  新式的手机看着真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  你要买手机么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果谁买了送给我我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这广阔的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有人愿意买任何东西给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  要走了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由乃  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「1月11日  冬日的剪贴画」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,画这些东西的时候知了还在大合唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.38,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暖阳庄）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得么  就是在小宫的房间里大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  记得记得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家新年好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  你这话我差不多听了十回了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天初诣的时候你就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（初诣：新年第一次参拜神社）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏神社不是那么拥挤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不用急急忙忙地参拜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是便装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野老师倒是穿着和服来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是cosplay女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过老师求到的签可是「凶」哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还打算将它放在嘴里用舌头打结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你的签是大吉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能因为这个而大意哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「好事多磨」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那中午见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的那堂课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说要换教室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,没听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（美术科  1-A）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寒假过得开心么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的寒假过得非常的充实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友褒电话粥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去唱卡拉OK啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年穿着漂亮的和服去参加初诣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到处躲着为了压岁钱来死缠烂打的侄儿侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 即使我向别人讨压岁钱也丝毫不为过的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们这样做真的很失礼是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始又会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:55.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,带了作业来的同学  请在下午的班会课之前交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很难得一副心不在焉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么忘记了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在再怎么拼命也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过会儿交不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候你的签不是大吉么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,等候的人会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,做生意  可盈利\N宜经商
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,打官司  胜诉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}纵横透视画法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的课就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业没有及时交…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想第一节实习课的时候能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我那时候交么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:06:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来「好事多磨」说的就是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到午休时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  去吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…去拿一下落在家里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫你先去食堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暖阳庄）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这些的话看着可能稍显单薄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（新年好  今年还请多多关照）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（我要加油！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新年好  今年还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个或许用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,copy来得及么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～  只有两分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终点就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好难为情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么班会课就到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪也积了不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家回家的时候要当心脚下哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（班会主题  联络事项  当心感冒）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业交晚了对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…是我的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回家后火速赶出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,午休的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐减肥所以分给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上是担心由乃赶不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从自己的饭团里给你留了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天轮到我们打扫卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点弄完了  去打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经积了这么厚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还谁的脚印都没有留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一大片的雪都可以一个人独享了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说今天轮到你们打扫卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得应该会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们帮忙么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  多谢好意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思这里就交给在下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,艺术创作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么过会儿见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我错过道谢的机会了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的首次创作活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Love & Peace吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是宫子的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P-I-E-C-E
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子还没有回来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正尽情地玩雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻还真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小时侯下雪了真是很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无条件的开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也根本没有心思去学习什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和由乃她们一样哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,堆雪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打雪仗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  也玩过雪橇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英那时很意外地是个普通人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说好象我现在是个怪人一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你小时侯也和现在一样cool呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很cool么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…寻你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很喜欢雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但不喜欢把自己弄得湿漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想  头发受潮后就像快要炸开来了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  实际上是想玩雪的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是喜欢在暖炉边上暖洋洋地待着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英你现在也是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是上了年纪么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,热茶真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭团的事我得去寻学姐那里道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫你是在期待什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是能有一杯热茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暖烘烘的炕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有点心和蜜橘我就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次新年的祝福问候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  那就是第十一回了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才回来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进来喝杯茶什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才正说起你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐的作业也拖到今天了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师布置的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不是当作作业的剪贴画…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你午休的时候在房间里做作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠推理啦  推理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后作业也及时地交上去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不会去玩雪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是敏锐的洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  这样像只猫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不热么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  挤死了挤死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经冻僵的身心都要融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐  什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  为什么是「碎片」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里写的是「PIECE」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说把我无限的爱化作碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送到世界的各个角落去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是写错了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想调查一下到底有百分之几的人能发现错误…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你刚说的不是不一样了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫你莫非不擅长英语
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  连这个都有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  小宫的兔子是茶色的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做得太投入不小心混进了土…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是野兔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个是摩艾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摩艾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：复活节岛上的巨大石像）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看着像是一个个的踏脚石而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是脑袋背对着我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这里面放了垃圾箱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一下这是我做的雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不错的作品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这么晚回来的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉做得太投入了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐你这照片是哪里拍的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在二层向阳的走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那实在是个不错的画面所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我中途回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而沙英可是一直在那里拍的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被偷拍了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么作为模特的报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我些茶  蜜橘和脆饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便再来些年糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桌上那些你先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福我倒是拍着不少好的素材了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要把这些做成剪贴画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天的实习课之前交上去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐还真能拖到最后关头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来得及就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  由乃你做的是怎么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,短信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}收到的短信001  前一条/后一条\N吉野屋老师\N由乃同学  你的作业我看了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  请喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学  你的作业我看了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说临时赶出来的  不过品位不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是把贺年片和照片做成剪贴画这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你选的素材非常的不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:16:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是素材好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你用的什么素材？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个地方用了吉野屋老师的贺年片的copy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…姿势不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到的贺年片是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到这份上也真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的cosplay之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有多少种呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是班上人手一种…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想收集了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是她的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这份无以言喻才是可怕之处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  另外一张贺年片呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前说的那张热热闹闹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是吉野屋老师么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贺年片收到了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在初梦里看见了那一天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（初梦：正月初一初二做的梦）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁发来的短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我去继续做剪贴画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻  谢谢你的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的饭团真的十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  寻同学的量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻在家里吃多了年糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要老是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始又要节食了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不努力可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多下来的食品  请务必给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你白天不也说过这个话么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻剩了一个饭团啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去的食堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃在这里做作业的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（今天的午餐菜单）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我还以为你真去拿落在家里的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要猪肉咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加量的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加料清汤面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻是两个饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后寻就对小宫说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「还是一样吃着这看起来热量很高的午饭呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫看着我的碟子说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「您的饭碗还真是轻飘飘呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是…你看…过年的时候年糕吃太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在家能饭来张口  真叫人感动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是问题所在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于不运动  热量一个劲地囤积
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一口咬下去就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,松松软软地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,松松软软…你听我说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底重了多少公斤什么的我都害怕得不敢问了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是正在问么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于这个原因又得稍微节食了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很出色地又把话题扯回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后寻学姐就剩了一个饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么「由乃肯定没有吃上午饭」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「这个就留给她吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是谢谢了  寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你可不能被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐是因为在节食才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,食物有剩余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就捐助给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想说这个的么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐对人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才这么说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃真是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是那么出色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃现在这个样子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连寻学姐都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁再下起来之前  去一下便利超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路上当心些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说有些早  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是乱七八糟一地的没有收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海之惠套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能中的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也发生了不少事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手有些变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得搽些护手霜去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,1月11日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:24.12,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}消えていつかは　儚い空へ上へ　声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.30,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}泡になって　消える　消える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:34.05,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}消える　消える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:37.46,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}それぞれの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:45.95,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}閃き　犇めきあう　融合して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:54.66,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}この身体は一つで　一つのようで　無限で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:23:04.23,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}零れ落ちた雫を　今掲げて見てるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:10.89,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}芽生えドライブ　走れ sky　裸足のまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:18.41,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}ほら目を瞑って　映りだした　虹の橋へ行こう!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:24.39,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}芽生えドライブ　照らす spark　砕けた星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:32.89,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}空に散りばめ　落ちてゆく　ひとかけらの夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:39.79,ED日文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}手に掴んだ　光を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:24.12,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}不知何时消逝的短暂天空中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.30,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}全化作泡沫　消失了　消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:34.05,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}消失了　消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:37.46,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}朝向各自不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:45.95,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}光芒闪耀　前簇后拥般　融合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:54.66,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}而这身体似乎像无限分散开来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:23:04.23,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}尝试托起落下的水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:10.89,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}萌芽着的行程　随心所欲地赤着脚奔向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:18.41,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}请你闭上眼　按心底所映出的　前往彩虹之桥!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:24.39,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}萌芽着的行程　照耀出火花　以及破碎的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:32.89,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}从空中散落　成为一块梦之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:39.79,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}被我将光茫紧握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些想知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.76,0:23:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天空为什么是蓝色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天为什么会觉得热？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易长大的薄荷叶为什么会有虫？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从什么地方传来了歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有地板在呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦开始想这些问题晚上都睡不着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做谜团套谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能的确有些棘手哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「8月21日  日本的夏日」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在暖阳庄里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.39,0:24:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来看哦
